('BIO 4415', 'Plant Physiology', 'Considers photosynthesis, material transport, seed germination, growth and development, flowering and fruiting, and hormones of plants. The relationship of structure and function will be emphasized. Includes laboratory. Typically offered: Autumn.   Fee(s): Biology Laboratory Fee', 5, 'W,UD', NULL, NULL, '[[[{"course_id": "BIO 2101", "min_grade": "C-", "concurrent_available": false}, {"course_id": "BIO 2103", "min_grade": "C-", "concurrent_available": false}]]]', NULL, 0),
