('MUS 2351', 'Wind Ensemble', 'As a group of selected wind, brass, and percussion players, this ensemble provides an opportunity for in-depth experience in the performance of wind ensemble and band repertoire. May be repeated an unlimited number of times.', 2, 'WKA', 'freshman,sophomore', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
